name: Blue Hello Kitty inspired iPhone 5/5S Case
description:
This custom made phone case is for my Hello Kitty loving divas and is sure to turn heads! This case is ONLY available for the iPhone 5/5S. 

It does not have a front snapping piece. ONLY a back cover.

This specific case's production time is 1/3 business days plus shipping. 

<B>
ALL ORDERS REQUIRE A SIGNATURE! If you do not want your package to require a signature, PLEASE CONTACT ME BEFORE PURCHASING!

<B>

<center> PLEASE READ BEFORE PURCHASING! </center>
**This is to inform all of my wonderful customers that ALL phone cases have been handmade by me, meaning there is a possibility of minor imperfections. Those imperfections may include glue around the rim of attached risen beads and glue residue. I will do my absolute best to remove all, but some will remain to insure the beads stay attached. Excessive dropping, putting into pocket or purse, or massive rubbing will cause gems to eventually loosen and may fall off over time. Just like anything else of value and beauty, please be careful with your case. Upon receiving this case you are giving acknowledgement of having read this disclaimer, and are aware, and agree that I cannot be held responsible for what has been stated above. THANK YOU!**
